[[Image:15-Puzzle.jpg|thumb|In the [[15 puzzle]] the goal is to get the squares in ascending order.  Initial positions which have an odd number of inversions are impossible to solve.&lt;ref name=&quot;Slocum&quot;&gt;{{cite web
  | last1     = Slocum
  | first1    = Jerry
